message.body: Long time no see. Think you'll be joining us tomorrow night? I'm pushing for queen of shiba after Desi. also, probably going to pbc brewery tour in the afternoon.
Hah why Q o S? Is Chris around tomorrow? Id be game for pbc.
Why weather dependant? Are you scooting?
Gotcha.
Ha you got it.
r that restaurant. What do you think? Ill be there either way.
Hey april is tired from work so ill probably just come to dinner, but I was thinking 7 pm might make more sense because we are a somewhat large group fo
No just me. She has school work and is tired from waiting tables. No pressure either way just a thought.
I guess changing the time might throw chris off. 730 is good if they have it.
For 730? So they take your name but don't reserve a space? Ah well, we shall see.
Ok. See you there.
Just had an irish potato. Intense, but delicious.
What were you thinking for tonight?
I have to ask: are seafood, mushrooms, or olives involved?
No worries. It is I who has the immature palette. Enjoy. Ill probably aim to get there around 845 or so. If you end up wanting some of what I mentioned o
n wednesday before the show, just let me know.
I just shopped at mariposa make sure tamara is proud of me!
She has it! But I still mainly use it for special purposes because of cost.
In case I forget, Chris wants us to let him know if we do anything after the show.
Who are you and what have you done with alex miler? I was going to do trolley, but now that choice makes me feel lazy.
There are no words.
I figure it takes about 25 minutes to walk from my place. I can meet you on my block or thereabouts at 820. Otherwise, we can meet there.
So you are coming here? Ill wait a couple more minutes just in case.
This is gross, but do you have your harmonica here? Think I could borrow it for a little?
I'm in center city right now, but at later date, sure.
Cool. Thanks.
Why, out of curiosity?
Mine is defective. I want to send it back but wanted one to hold me over until the replacement arrives.
After all those online reviews. Damn them.
A few people said they had some problems. The same that I'm having.
Nope, in new york for the night.
Thanks.
Already have similar plans elsewhere, but will definitely rain check!
It's the only option, really.
Happy birthday sir. Ill give you your gift next time I see you. hope you feel refreshed and alive after the run.
Awww cool.
If you are in the neighborhood tonight, I can give you your birthday present.
Or sometime this weekend when you are nearby.
Tomorrow afternoon, perhaps. We'll see how the day goes.
Nope.
Should be home around five. Will let you know.
Will be home in about ten. You can stop by or I can come to you. either way is fine.
Here I come.
Ha! Classic. I haven't seen April in a few days so I'm gonna chill with her but have fun! Drink some yuengling.
You around? We're chilling at Alex's for his bday.
Thanks but I'm out tonight. Enjoy!
